  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Residence Le Coeur des Loges has an excellent location in <a data-udi="umb://document/4eae720ba8984d83a83f530983b4b6f8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4eae720ba8984d83a83f530983b4b6f8}" title="Les Menuires">Les Menuires</a>, you have all the necessities closeby, as well as ski in, ski out access to the Three Valleys. After a day on the slopes, you can reserve a space in the lovely wellness centre - perfect for unwinding and giving your achy ski legs a rest. </p>
<h2>Piste side location</h2>
<p><span>Given that the resort is purpose built it has all of the necessities needed for a great stay, along with fantastic access to the wider <a data-udi="umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578" href="/{localLink:umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578}" title="Three Valleys Ski Area">Three Valleys Ski Area</a>. </span>Located at the entrance to <a data-udi="umb://document/4eae720ba8984d83a83f530983b4b6f8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4eae720ba8984d83a83f530983b4b6f8}" title="Les Menuires">Les Menuires</a>, the Coeur des Loges is the ideal place for groups and families as the apartments combine modern convenience with traditional Alpine décor. With ski-in/ski-out access these apartments are perfect for the keen skiers and boarders who wish to get first lifts.</p>
<h2>Soothing spa</h2>
<p>The property features an indoor pool and spa area with a hot tub, sauna and hammam on a reservation only basis, perfect for soaking away your achy ski legs or for when its just too snowy to ski. You can enjoy an afternoon of relaxation before 4pm, after this time entry is payable locally.</p>
<h2>Family friendly</h2>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/4eae720ba8984d83a83f530983b4b6f8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4eae720ba8984d83a83f530983b4b6f8}" title="Les Menuires">Les Menuires</a> is a great place for the whole family, there are extensive beginner slopes in the local area for those just starting out, or a vast choice of red runs across the ski area for the more confident skier or boarder. The residence provides free kids and teen clubs throughout the winter, where children can enjoy making new friends while playing games and taking part in activities both inside and outside. For the teens, there is a games room with a flat screen TV, PlayStation 4 and virtual reality headsets. </p>]]></description>
