  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>One bedroom comfort apartments</strong> can sleep up to four people and are 32 - 38m². The apartments have a twin bedroom and a living room with double sofa bed.</p>
<p><strong>Two bedroom family apartments </strong>can sleep up to six people and are 38 - 45m². There's a living room with a double sofa bed, twin bedroom and a small cabin bedroom with bunk beds. Most apartments have an additional shower room.</p>
<p><strong>Two bedroom comfort apartments</strong> can sleep up to six people and are 47 - 55m². These apartments are larger with living room with a double sofa bed, two twin bedrooms and an additional shower room.</p>
<p><strong>Three bedroom apartments</strong> can sleep up to eight people and are around 70m². These apartments have a living room with a double sofa bed, two twin bedrooms and either a smaller bedroom with bunkbeds or additional twin bedroom, and an additional shower room. </p>
<p><strong>Apartment facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Lounge with TV</li>
<li>Fireplace</li>
<li>Balcony or terrace</li>
<li>Kitchenette equipped with ceramic hob, dishwasher, microwave oven combi, kettle, filter coffee machine, fridge</li>
<li>Bath with shower head attachment or shower room</li>
<li>Separate WC</li>
<li>Heated towel rail</li>
<li>Hairdryer </li>
<li>Bed linen and towels</li>
<li>Cleaning kit</li>
<li>Beds are made on arrival (except sofa beds)</li>
<li>End of stay cleaning is included (except kitchen)</li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
